                                <p>卷軸</p>
                                <decoNote>
                                    Handscroll with wide borders (大鑲手卷): The protective and decorative backing (錦包首) is crafted from
                                    blue silk adorned with gilt patterns of clouds. The title label (題簽) is composed of pink Chinese paper. 
                                    The 'Heaven' section (天) is fashioned from pale blue silk. Vertical stripes (隔水) feature silk of 
                                    white and pale-yellow colours. Borders (邊) are made of white silk. The frontispiece (引首) and colophon 
                                    section (拖尾) are crafted from traditional Chinese paper. 
                                    大鑲手卷。錦包首為藍色帶金色祥雲花紋絲織物，題簽為淡粉色紙本，有破損痕跡，八寶帶為藍色，別子已丟失。天為淺藍色絲織物，
                                    隔水與副隔水為白色和淺黃色絲織物，邊為白色絲織物，引首和拖尾為米白色紙本。</decoNote>
